summary: I woke up extra soft for Dan today. I love that dork so much. I love his hyena laugh and his soft “hello”s. And his prayer hands...
body:
I woke up extra soft for Dan today. I love that dork so much. I love his hyena laugh and his soft “hello”s. And his prayer hands when he gets excited. I love that he’s so passionate about being the best possible version of himself. I love that he cares so deeply and gets too invested. I hope he’s still aware of how much he’s loved by the people in this community.



But you bastards better not say anything or tell him that….I have a reputation here!

summary: No shade to Dan at all. But he sure is lucky to be able to step away from what is essentially his job for so long. Who knows...
body: No shade to Dan at all. But he sure is lucky to be able to step away from what is essentially his job for so long. Who knows what he’s doing behind the scenes but as of now I think we are granted to assume he is just resting himself and figuring things out. Which is great for him but I envy that life a little. A lot of people get severely, and I mean SEVERELY, depressed but they can’t take a break in their lives because they can’t afford to just not work. Many people like myself live from paycheck to paycheck and every day of work counts which means no sulking in bed for a day if you’re feeling out of it. I’m happy for Dan to have that luxury to do this but my green demon does come out a little bit and wish I could have that, too.
